{"tid":910101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解D港女行山 可以行到隻狗都唔見左?","createTime":"2018-11-21T02:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T16:10:26.000Z","uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":65,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"1bbe424a841a7b05b416b3d11e636cd28ff097ad","tid":910101,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:01:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">子華神：兩個愛護動物的人去拍攝非洲大笨象的生活。那些大笨象是真的大笨的，走著走著，是會不記得有一隻小笨象。而小笨象也不是小笨的，那麼大群大笨象走著走著都會不見了。於是小笨象就會周圍去找大笨象，一直都找不到</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唐狗忌廉獅子山郊野公園走失　主人連日搜山：我唔想放棄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2105349/org/6f0b82895169f3d1efe875c33b40226f.jpg/BqVjCEiKi14aBh2hCIbSlWnH7JdCcKSryVfoGMlX6Bg?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2105349%2Forg%2F6f0b82895169f3d1efe875c33b40226f.jpg%2FBqVjCEiKi14aBh2hCIbSlWnH7JdCcKSryVfoGMlX6Bg%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=76a6b385&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一頭7歲多的唐狗周二（13日）於獅子山郊野公園走失，主人全家總動員尋狗。其中一位主人陳小姐特地告假，一天尋狗近14小時；她更稱父親有兩晚通宵守在郊野公園，徹夜不眠地等待愛犬，可惜仍一無所獲。由於走失現場的其中一邊是山坡，陳小姐正呼籲有經驗的行山人士幫忙尋狗。<br />\n<br />\n陳小姐接受《香港01》訪問時表示，「忌廉」是頭棕黑色唐狗，本周二在獅子山郊野公園走失，年齡約 7歲多。陳小姐父親在事發當日帶「忌廉」到山中散步，雖然「忌廉」有晶片及當時戴有螢光綠色的頸圈，但並沒有上狗繩。<br />\n<br />\n原地等候3小時仍不見愛犬蹤影<br />\n<br />\n當陳的父親走到衛奕信徑5段的附近時，回頭一看赫然發現「忌廉」失蹤。他原以為「忌廉」只是貪玩落後，便站在原地等牠。陳小姐稱，陳父在原地等了3個小時，但仍不見「忌廉」影蹤，於是折返起點。陳父途中一直不見「忌廉」，遂致電家人。陳小姐及其家人到場後，高呼「忌廉」的名字，可惜牠一直沒有出現。<br />\n<br />\n陳父原以為「忌廉」只是貪玩而落後，但3小時後仍不見牠回來。（受訪者提供）<br />\n<br />\n接下來的3天，陳小姐及胞弟特地告假，每天四出尋狗，一天搜索近14小時。陳小姐亦指，父親有兩晚通宵守在郊野公園涼亭，徹夜不眠地等待「忌廉」出現。他們更廣貼告示，從獅子山郊野公園附近到大圍一帶均有張貼，希望有市民能幫忙尋狗。<br />\n<br />\n狗主：狗狗非常熟路　迷路可能性不大<br />\n<br />\n陳小姐表示父親數年來都會帶「忌廉」到此散步，「忌廉」已非常熟路，認為迷路的可能性不大；她補充，最擔心愛犬因受傷而被困山中。因走失現場的其中一邊是山坡，陳小姐曾向消防處求助，消防員到場搜索了半小時後便收隊離去。雖然尋回愛犬的希望越來越渺茫，陳小姐哽咽道：「唔敢諗搵唔搵到，但我唔想就咁放棄。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然尋回愛犬的希望越來越渺茫，但陳小姐不想就此放棄。（受訪者提供）<br />\n<br />\n因走失現場地勢不平坦，一般人要在該地尋狗並不容易，因此陳小姐希望呼籲有經驗的行山人士幫忙。如有任何人有「忌廉」消息，或是願意協助尋狗，可以致電9248 8566聯絡陳小姐。"},{"pid":"f9f31a5428a7796fa398d369f303f46c8738c2fb","tid":910101,"uid":170045,"like":95,"dislike":1,"score":94,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:04:51.000Z","msg":"有時啲友唔用狗帶 隻狗又活力充沛"},{"pid":"c93764a5daa5c6bb125084076953d4a68b0846d2","tid":910101,"uid":163081,"like":144,"dislike":0,"score":144,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:05:38.000Z","msg":"唔係港女個老豆帶狗行山咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7fde06cf6f72e87931c64757c0a376d5d106c59","tid":910101,"uid":90499,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:06:52.000Z","msg":"神仙都企唔穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e682f68009390e4b9ed0d1f8a3a0fcaeab779f","tid":910101,"uid":139065,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:06:58.000Z","msg":"港女個老豆喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6057de47d7cc52ff975a94e37c66d409305598","tid":910101,"uid":166827,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:10:16.000Z","msg":"標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1aedca734a935fc1524f039e551f33da1b51ef7","tid":910101,"uid":197337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:11:02.000Z","msg":"咩叫數年來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  , 一年行1,2次可以叫數年來,1日行1次都可以叫數年來"},{"pid":"2a2e7638919d79bbfbe24febf8a98566357dc1fd","tid":910101,"uid":73613,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:11:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"083f28215363828c8634642fde0f584cb337d58b","tid":910101,"uid":18251,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7fde06cf6f72e87931c64757c0a376d5d106c59","tid":910101,"uid":90499,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:06:52.000Z","msg":"神仙都企唔穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:23:42.000Z","msg":"唐狗、黑色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e7b7a3bb3c14f158da1531044cfea651f8f18f","tid":910101,"uid":145779,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:27:04.000Z","msg":"唔拖狗繩 此po已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2697a79c5204ee025a67c4d1bb378525c11bca","tid":910101,"uid":65887,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"083f28215363828c8634642fde0f584cb337d58b","tid":910101,"uid":18251,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7fde06cf6f72e87931c64757c0a376d5d106c59","tid":910101,"uid":90499,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:06:52.000Z","msg":"神仙都企唔穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:23:42.000Z","msg":"唐狗、黑色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:32:58.000Z","msg":"三六<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37eaad75366841d8b1aa35231ce68638252560ba","tid":910101,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:38:14.000Z","msg":"隻豬有無唔見到? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d54d689898dc51ac54c6ffb1edcb5faa80f2623","tid":910101,"uid":192517,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:54:06.000Z","msg":"個標題做乜鳩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dccefbe8803ee8b0ab61e2d48113a07b99f441b","tid":910101,"uid":192517,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"37eaad75366841d8b1aa35231ce68638252560ba","tid":910101,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"re